pdfspine — bundled Liberation fonts NOTICE
==========================================

This product includes the Liberation font family (Liberation Sans, Liberation
Serif, Liberation Mono — Regular / Bold / Italic / BoldItalic), embedded into
the renderer as permissive substitute glyph outlines for the non-embedded
standard-14 text fonts (Helvetica / Times / Courier and their metric-compatible
aliases Arial / Times New Roman / Courier New).

